        "TileImage": "$($repository 671746f4-eecd-417d-b0cd-1ad49e88f0c2).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning 47. Today you return to Santa Fortuna, where we have three really tough targets. So our client was once a rich man who lived happily with his wife for years, years ago. In time, however, it was revealed that the woman cheated on him, and robbed him of his money. In the end, the wife ran away with almost all of the man&apos;s wealth. Now the man wants revenge. Our client wants you to murder his ex-wife, his new husband, and his wife&apos;s very long and loyal friend. Have fun!",
